headline: Merck Animal Health and State of Kansas Announce $895 Million Investment in Manufacturing and Research & Development Facilities in De Soto
summary: RAHWAY, N.J., May 08, 2025--Merck Animal Health, known as MSD Animal Health outside of the United States and Canada, a division of Merck & Co., Inc., Rahway, N.J., USA (NYSE: MRK), and Kansas Governor Laura Kelly jointly announced today the $895 million expansion of Merck Animal Health’s manufacturing facility in De Soto, Kansas.
